text: New weekly cases among nursing home residents rose nearly four-fold from the end of May to late October, from 1,083 to 4,274, according to an Associated Press analysis of federal data from 20 states. https://t.co/Ee5acO9rUY

text: Joe Biden announced the two co-chairs of the incoming administration’s task force: Vivek Murthy, a former U.S. surgeon general, and David Kessler, a former commissioner of the Food and Drug Administration. https://t.co/4V0QdcMCfY

name: sfchronicle
text: “When he got to college he saw a lack of representation for people like him,” said Lauren Ashe of Mill Valley, who met Lee in 2014 during his first campaign — for the student senate at Davis. Lee won that office, then won the next year for president. https://t.co/mb7NZ8U1Uy

name: sfchronicle
text:
Joe Biden's German shepherd Major will make history as the White House’s first shelter dog.

And the Bay Area is here for it. https://t.co/tm0V0Rtwzz

name: sfchronicle
text:
Kamala Harris.
First woman elected VP.
First Black person elected VP.
First Asian American elected VP.
First Black senator from California.
First woman and Black person to be California AG.
First woman and person of color to serve as S.F. DA. https://t.co/zfVVxS84ak

name: sfchronicle
text: “I knocked on 30,000 doors, and that relationship-building paid off,” Lee said Sunday morning while driving between events. His new job doesn’t start for a month, but he is already at work full time. https://t.co/2KcL0Wech9

name: sfchronicle
text: “I’m proud, ecstatic, happy. I’m going from jumping for joy to tears,” said Oakland resident Dezie Woods-Jones, 78, a long-time civil rights leader and state president of Black Woman Organized for Political Action, who has known Harris for decades. https://t.co/koHSrazs8q

name: sfchronicle
text: “A weight has been lifted from my shoulders,” said San Francisco resident Alison Kirk, who was walking her dog Olive shortly after the news hit the airwaves. “It’s a relief I won’t be embarrassed by my president 50 times a day.” https://t.co/Dl7UAHJsWn
